<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Ruthful" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ruthful,</orth> piteous: <cit><quote>that my death would stay these r. deeds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.5.95" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 5, 95</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>this r. piece of butchery,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.3.5" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 3, 5</bibl></cit> (Qq <emph>ruthless</emph>). <cit><quote>spur them to r. work,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.3.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 3, 48</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>villanies r. to hear,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.1.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 1, 66</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>